Package com.stbasarab.collections

Class DoublyLinkedList<T>

java.lang.Object
com.stbasarab.collections.DoublyLinkedList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - the type of elements stored in the list
public class DoublyLinkedList<T> extends Object
A generic doubly linked list implementation. This class allows for dynamic storage and manipulation of elements.
